ineruniface_104ujg1665702668574.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ujg1665702668574.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ujg1665702668574.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ujg1665702668574\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__deleteattributes_431266\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Delete the specified session attributes.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__topic_d131891e1_d131892e1_d131893e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ujg1665702668574_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__codeblock_vkz_dkd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"DeleteAttributes\",AttributeList</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__topic_d93652e1_d93653e1_d93654e1_d93655e1_d93656e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d798298e58\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__p_d131900e1_d131901e1_d131902e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AttributeList</var>—string (or variable or parameter evaluating to a string) containing one or more session attribute names, separated by semicolons. The attribute names are user-defined and case-sensitive. If omitted, no attributes are deleted.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__topic_d93657e1_d93658e1_d93659e1_d93660e1_d93661e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d798298e70\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__p_d131906e1_d131907e1_d131908e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DeleteAttributes</span> is executed on\n            the current session. If the previous <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ChangeSession</span> command was a\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">CLOSE</code> action, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DeleteAttributes</span> command is\n            ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__section_abf_gkd_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d798298e90\">Example: Deleting Session Attributes</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ujg1665702668574_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ujg1665702668574__codeblock_wgc_3kd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putitem /id $webinfo ( \"SESSIONCOMMANDS\" ), \"DeleteAttributes\", \"DATA1;Data2\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532711\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532711\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DeleteAttributes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete the specified session attributes. Explain this code $webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"DeleteAttributes\",AttributeList Copy Parameters AttributeList —string (or variable or parameter evaluating to a string) containing one or more session attribute names, separated by semicolons. The attribute names are user-defined and case-sensitive. If omitted, no attributes are deleted. Description DeleteAttributes is executed on the current session. If the previous ChangeSession command was a CLOSE action, the DeleteAttributes command is ignored. Example: Deleting Session Attributes Explain this code putitem /id $webinfo ( \"SESSIONCOMMANDS\" ), \"DeleteAttributes\", \"DATA1;Data2\" Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}